title: Try!
description: Huget looks to be in for a fraction of a second but he is dragged down short. France recycle; it goes left and the giant replacement lock rides one tackle and goes over!

title: Full-time
description: Well well well that was all a little bit exciting in the end. A brilliant defensive effort from the home side
